Package: rasterTools
Title: obtain and process earth observation data
Version: 0.6
Authors@R: person("Steffen", "Ehrmann", email = "steffen.rasterTools@funroll-loops.de",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2958-0796"))
Description: The rasterTools package provides the toolchain for a transparent 
    and reproducible workflow to obtain and process spatial (earth observation)
    data for an evidence based approach to landscape ecological questions.
